@node intro "Was ist das ?"
This pack features 16 colors icons inspired by Trevor Morris ones (The original MWB only uses 8 colors). if you find your Workbench/Opus Gloomy, Horrible,... Before going for Newicons (which is only useful with a graphic CARD in my opinion), try my art stuff and tell me what you think'bout it.
@endnode

@node inst "How to install it"
Change you screenmode to 16 colors and then change the colors as @{" following... " link "palette"}
@endnode

@node palette "Setting the 16 colors"
@font XEN.font 11
Use your MWB-Deamon or whatever palette tool to lock the colors 4 to 11.

0. [@{bpen 0}  @{bpen 0}]  Background   -> 149,149,149   9. [@{bpen 9}  @{bpen 0}]  Antrahzit    ->  40, 62, 91
1. [@{bpen 1}  @{bpen 0}]  Black        ->   0,  0,  0  10. [@{bpen 10}  @{bpen 0}]  Green        ->  96,128, 96
2. [@{bpen 2}  @{bpen 0}]  White        -> 255,255,255  11. [@{bpen 11}  @{bpen 0}]  Yellow       -> 226,209,119
3. [@{bpen 3}  @{bpen 0}]  Blue         ->  59,103,162  12  [@{bpen 12}  @{bpen 0}]  Brightrose   -> 255,212,203
4. [@{bpen 4}  @{bpen 0}]  Med.grey     -> 123,123,123  13. [@{bpen 13}  @{bpen 0}]  Brown        -> 122, 96, 72
5. [@{bpen 5}  @{bpen 0}]  BrightgreyI  -> 175,175,175  14. [@{bpen 14}  @{bpen 0}]  Brightgrey   -> 210,210,210
6. [@{bpen 6}  @{bpen 0}]  Brightbrown  -> 170,144,124  15. [@{bpen 15}  @{bpen 0}]  Red          -> 229, 93, 93
7. [@{bpen 7}  @{bpen 0}]  Rose         -> 255,169,151
8. [@{bpen 8}  @{bpen 0}]  Darkgrey     ->  80, 80, 80  <- itīs a new definition at this Time
@endnode

